author: Headbaenger
title: Great Set!
review:
I bought this set for 31€. And it is worth it. But I don't think, I would have bought it for 49,99€.

It's playability is astonishing and the building experience is really great. I can't say anything about the parts.

Foremost I like all the details and the scale of the model. It is a really smart construction.
